## Nominal Derivational Morphology {#sec:nounderiv}

* V → N
    * [Morpheme rinmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:rinmlz) ‘action <span class=""smallcaps"">nmlz</span>’
    * [Morpheme jpenmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:jpenmlz)
        * ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">PST.ABS.nmlz</span>’
        * ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">PST</span>.ACT.<span class=""smallcaps"">nmlz</span>?’ 
    * ?[Morpheme neinf](MorphsetTable?#cldf:neinf) ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">inf</span> / generic action nominalizer’
        * Not only on intransitive verbs? see *wanumanë* 'gossip, lie' and *wajtënë* 'dance' 
    * [Morpheme ninmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:ninmlz) ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">a.nmlz</span>’
    * [Morpheme nnmlzpre](MorphsetTable?#cldf:nnmlzpre) ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">p.nmlz</span>’
        * [Morpheme nnmlzpre](MorphsetTable?#cldf:nnmlzpre)V[Morpheme rinmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:rinmlz)    ‘nonpast?’
        * ?? [Morpheme nnmlzpre](MorphsetTable?#cldf:nnmlzpre)V[Morpheme jpepst](MorphsetTable?#cldf:jpepst)    ‘past?’
    * [Morpheme sapenmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:sapenmlz) ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">ABS.nmlz</span>’ (contrast with ‑jpë )
    * [Morpheme toponmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:toponmlz) ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">circ.nmlz</span>’
    * [Morpheme pininmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:pininmlz) ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">priv.nmlz</span>’ ?
* Adv → N 
