    * Ø‑ '<span class=""smallcaps"">3s</span>' with intransitive verbs
    *   • exception: *ij‑të‑ri* ‘he goes’ plus 2 more <span title='which ones?'>❓</span>
    * Ø‑ ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">3p</span>’ with transitive verbs with <span class=""smallcaps"">1a</span> or <span class=""smallcaps"">2a</span>; also sometimes <span class=""smallcaps"">3a</span>
    * [Morpheme t3](MorphsetTable?#cldf:t3) ‘<span class=""smallcaps"">3>3</span>’
        * Not required, but possible
            * Check: not in alternation with preceding O NP?
